# -- Tree id: aetherhaven_blacksmith (Garren Vale) --
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_abandoned.body=No grudge. If you still want smoke in town, ask again.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_abandoned.c0=Fair enough.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_abandoned.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_building.body=When the shop is built, I will walk to the weapon bench and set up. Come find me there and we will call it done.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_building.c0=I need to drop the quest.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_building.c1=I will keep at it.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_building.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_done.body=Solid bench. The heat will come when the work does. We are not shipping ore across the map anymore. We use what this ground still gives.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_done.c0=Hammer well.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_done.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_accepted.body=When the place is up, put my name on the block inside, then come find me. I want to hear you say it out loud.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_accepted.c0=You'll hear it.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_accepted.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_finish.body=Good. A roof that does not smell like someone else's stew.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_finish.c0=Enjoy it.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_finish.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_offer.body=The shop earns me blisters. I still want a roof I do not borrow. Same house plot as anyone. Register me when the walls are real.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_offer.c0=I'll stake a house.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_offer.c1=Another time.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_offer.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_remind.body=Iron does not rush. When the house is done, register me, then come talk. That is when we are even.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_remind.c0=Understood.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_house_remind.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_quest_shop.body=Corin's boards are fine for sleep. They are lousy for a hammer swing. Stake a blacksmith shop with walls, a counter, and a weapon bench I can own. Craft the plot token at your planning desk, place it with your staff, and pay the sign. When it stands, meet me at the bench.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_quest_shop.c0=We'll get it built.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_quest_shop.c1=Not right now.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_quest_shop.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_shop_accepted.body=Good. I will camp at the inn until the chimney tells the truth. Then find me at the bench and we will close the ledger.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_shop_accepted.c0=See you there.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.garren_shop_accepted.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.rep_reward_25.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.rep_reward_50.speaker=Garren Vale
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.body=Garren Vale. Wind is low enough that the forge might behave. Metal this far out has opinions. I am here to argue with it.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c2=You wanted to talk about a house.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c3=Your name is on the block. I figured you should hear it.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c4=The house is still in progress.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c5=Good to see you working the steel.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c6=The shop is built. The bench is ready.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c7=About the forge build...
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c8=You said you needed a real forge here.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.c9=Mind your fingers.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_blacksmith.root.speaker=Garren Vale
# -- Tree id: aetherhaven_dialogue_test (QA / harness) --
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_dialogue_test.conditions_lab.body=Conditions lab. You should not see a hidden choice. You should see a greyed choice. Use the compound gates to continue.
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_dialogue_test.conditions_lab.c0=This choice is hidden (literal false).
aetherhaven.dialogue.aetherhaven_dialogue_test.conditions_lab.c1=This should be greyed out.
